The following is an incomplete list of people that have contributed to this 
project in some way or another, in no particular order...

	David Odin, for having written very good articles (in Linux Mag France)
	and an even better reference book about GTK+.

	Tigert (Tuomas Kuosmanen), for creating the nice Beaver logo you can
	see when you display the 'About' window.

	Jimmac for creating the wonderful toolbar icons.

	Our other artist, Emmanuel's brother Remy, who created our Website's
	Beaver logo.

	Ramakrishnan M., our Debian maintainer, for allowing our little editor
	to be part of the greatest distribution of all.
